sequenceDiagram
    participant D as UWB Device
    participant B as Backend
    participant P as Processing
    participant N as Notifications
    participant A as App

    D->>B: Raw Data (1Hz)
    B->>P: Stream Processing
    P->>B: Processed Data
    P->>N: Trigger Alert
    N->>A: Push Notification
    A->>B: Fetch Details
    B->>A: Return Data
